attributes.body: Huaraz has been a gas. Mostly due to my new Dutch buddies. I rode here from Huanchaco with the Dutchies in a car along side. The ride was mostly beautiful, and once again gave me an impressive cross section view of the geography of Peru. This time though, we landed in the true complete opposite of where we started. We went from hot beaches, to snow capped peaks, all in a day's ride. Incredible.

photos.title: Cory on Motorcycle
photos.description: Riding to Huaraz, stopped at a construction zone.

photos.title: Dutchies and Chicken
photos.description: I traveled with my two new dutch friends. They are a barrel of laughs at any given moment, for any given circumstance.

photos.title: Polleria Diana
photos.description: In this restaurant you order a half or quarter of a chicken. Those are all of the choices. They were great!

photos.title: Rock Wall
photos.description: It's much taller than this photo makes it look.

photos.title: Dirt Bridge Panorama
photos.description: One of the first lakes encountered.

photos.title: Rick with Cow
photos.description: Rick is here demonstrating how to approach a cow, if one were trying to snuggle up for warmth. He did not succeed.

photos.title: Waterfall
photos.description: I think this is the coldest waterfall I've seen on my trip, and I've seen a great many waterfalls.

photos.title: Dutchies
photos.description: My hiking buddies for the day. There was much laughter.

photos.title: Charging
photos.description: Team Netherlands charging up the mountain like pros.

photos.title: First Glimpse of Lake 69
photos.description: When you're walking up towards Lake 69 this is the first little glimpse you get.

photos.title: Blue Lagoon
photos.description: It was impossible to fit all of the glory in one frame.

photos.title: Victory Pose
photos.description: We were definitely the only ones with a bottle of champagne at the top... Though, it was terrible champagne.

photos.title: Cory Pose
photos.description: Come and get it ladies. I'll be waiting with a bottle of champagne and a wheel of cheese.

photos.title: Mountain Stream
photos.description: This thing was rolling down the mountain crazy fast.
